:"recxDEP8UZTymLeVj","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3WEGPl0a1PS0cC","target":"recEtYuMAHI6UAK8P","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3WEGPl0a1PS0cC","target":"recGdQVod5SbLO87Z","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3WEGPl0a1PS0cC","target":"recIF1Q0gHP65ziSy","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3WEGPl0a1PS0cC","target":"recCnbP6ZTjAmPCnR","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3WEGPl0a1PS0cC","target":"recE4R1DFGiDMLM5y","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3WEGPl0a1PS0cC","target":"recRShKfG3aDWnBy5","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec3WEGPl0a1PS0cC","target":"reczKwHT81lCIivSq","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec3pQvMwnq8Vpimi","ref":"Neh.1.1","text":"The words of Nehemiah the son of Hachaliah. And it came to pass in the month Chisleu, in the twentieth year, as I was in Shushan the palace,","year":-457},{"id":"recL8pQbvWKnRXdJJ","ref":"Neh.1.2","text":"That Hanani, one of my brethren, came, he and certain men of Judah; and I asked them concerning the Jews that had escaped, which were left of the captivity, and concerning Jerusalem.","year":-457},{"id":"recPCCDh4Lx2WHTjb","ref":"Neh.1.3","text":"And they said unto me, The remnant that are left of the captivity there in the province are in great affliction and reproach: the wall of Jerusalem also is broken down, and the gates thereof are burned with fire.","year":-457},{"id":"recHXMoUaAIQfcHe3","ref":"Neh.1.4","text":"And it came to pass, when I heard these words, that I sat down and wept, and mourned certain days, and fasted, and prayed before the God of heaven,","year":-457},{"id":"recEXKTOXfc86l9v0","ref":"Neh.1.5","text":"And said, I beseech thee, O LORD God of heaven, the great and terrible God, that keepeth covenant and mercy for them that love him and observe his commandments:","year":-457},{"id":"recj8yvfc4Xa7LmcV","ref":"Neh.1.6","text":"Let thine ear now be attentive, and thine eyes open, that thou mayest hear the prayer of thy servant, which I pray before thee now, day and night, for the children of Israel thy servants, and confess the sins of the children of Israel, which we have sinned against thee: both I and my father’s house have sinned.","year":-457}]}
